Data used to geocode the point field,
Proximity to other Store instances, determined via point to point
comparison, will add newly imported Store to the similar_stores
field of every proximal Store. This field determines left column
Stores in the merge interface (ones with similar_stores) and right
column Stores (the foreign key target Stores.) This proximal
match must be resolved in one of the ways above.
